{
  "id": "RAW_7c4abe3d",
  "title": "不会封号的 Claude Code 使用方法！已稳定测试一个月，还能共享给团队。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247500368&idx=1&sn=2d8b7e327f3b01f489e7f317d12da77d",
  "date": "2026-01-13 16:31:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8ca58dc2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BFZjTT7pnzpsphBMfk453hcyyicM127hoYfJdX9WGERV3DEXdjFp3xkAg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"padding: 20px 24px 56px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0px auto;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;background-color: rgb(250, 249, 247) !important;text-align: left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用Claude Code最大的痛点是什么？其实不是贵，而是封号。因为就算使用Claude Max Plan 每月$200美金，虽然看上去贵，但是一个月能轻松用上价值数千美金甚至上万美金的token，是很便宜的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">相信大家都被Claude Code封号折磨得不行。那如何可以不封号呢？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">前段时间我提过，有一个办法可以不被封号，有些朋友可以没注意到，我单独再写一篇。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个方法我已经使用过较长时间了，还共享给了团队同事使用，都完全没问题。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前我团队同时有官方的Claude Code Max Plan、也有通过下面方法使用的Claude Code，经过一个多月的长期对比，发现没有区别。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">为啥没有区别？因为用的是官方的Claude Code客户端 + 满血版的Claude Code API啊！唯一区别是Claude Code API不来自Claude Code Max Plan。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;margin: 56px 0px 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(193, 95, 60) 0%, rgb(157, 200, 141) 100%) text;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: inherit !important;background-color: transparent !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">省流版步骤</span></strong></h2>\n   <ol style=\"margin: 32px 0px;padding-left: 32px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">购买Google AI Ultra或者Google AI Pro套餐，可以在Google Antigravity里同时使用Gemini 3 Pro、Gemini 3 Flash、Claude Opus 4.5、Claude Sonnet 4.5</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过工具（如：Antigravity Tools），把Google Antigravity的Claude系列模型变成API</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过API的方式使用官方正版Claude Code客户端即可，非常稳定，不用担心封号（因为<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">正常渠道付费</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">的Google AI Ultra套餐几乎从不封号</span>）。无论是Claude Code CLI还是Claude Code VS Extension均可以。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">下图是该方法使用Claude Code CLI的截图</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5981481481481481\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12) 0px 8px 32px;max-height: 600px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016703\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=32fcb644&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BFegMg7OVJbhNsOMtYYyrX8pyDG4CFZysgd6J72ARQD3aibnpfAt4N2Mg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">下图是该方法使用Claude Code VS Extension的截图</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5731481481481482\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12) 0px 8px 32px;max-height: 600px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016702\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a6d48d06&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BFhxibjVRBYeJsicibQiadswZo0cUUXib8bPnar8wrVde9bIkk7S2BSLQHiaicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;margin: 56px 0px 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(193, 95, 60) 0%, rgb(157, 200, 141) 100%) text;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: inherit !important;background-color: transparent !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">展开讲讲</span></strong></h2>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;margin: 48px 0px 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: inherit !important;background-color: transparent !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一步：购买Google AI Ultra或者Google AI Pro套餐</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">推荐使用前者，表面上贵，实际上不贵。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你实在是比较拮据，你可以购买Google AI Pro，在闲鱼上成品号一年才几十块钱人民币，可以多买几个，通过工具自动管理、自动轮换。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;margin: 48px 0px 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: inherit !important;background-color: transparent !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二步：下载Antigravity Tools，把Google Antigravity的能力变成API</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">下载地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/lbjlaq/Antigravity-Manager/releases\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/lbjlaq/Antigravity-Manager/releases</a></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">安装适合你操作系统的最新版本。无论什么操作系统，都支持，有对应的版本。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">下载后，点击添加账号，登录上你在第一步准备好的账号</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.662962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12) 0px 8px 32px;max-height: 600px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016704\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=534f2339&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BF1XXrX8QxiaRzbRqxXqPptwnbFpfhgaiapoBggG1HIPkTeWUPge3ic32icA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里是面板统计</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.662962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12) 0px 8px 32px;max-height: 600px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016705\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3696869b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BF7zpUiaHcglZGMtUHFYRa6XwLB5IEw9I6z0dh5m69Y46wurPoo06BlwA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里是各种模型能力被变成了API，支持多种主流协议。这里我们选择Anthropic协议</span></p>\n   <table style=\"width: 100% !important;border-collapse: collapse !important;margin: 20px auto !important;table-layout: fixed !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.662962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;border-radius: 4px !important;object-fit: contain !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016706\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=72464cfd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BF36bc71icyPLKJeqNdNQuqoibiaXhaqZzl3Gcf11vBtrjSmkhFIBiaanfBA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.662962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;border-radius: 4px !important;object-fit: contain !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016709\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=abfc0fca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BFXc4sk4cPhXO1w7K7pcR0CicqKiaic3lqwBx5qEunt3ANOicib3mKdt1tgrg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;margin: 48px 0px 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: inherit !important;background-color: transparent !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">第三步：把上图Claude 4.5 Opus(Thinking)的API接入Claude Code</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">点击复制，获取API示例代码</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.662962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12) 0px 8px 32px;max-height: 600px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016708\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=58ace6ee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BFjqRKjwdoKsN2CN97ytUUCy3ELqg7x3tLGtAbpbKhbicSV04zdvicVG2Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">自动配置：然后打开一个AI Agent(推荐Codex)，让它自动配置</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">大致的Prompt如下，请你自己改一下，改成你的本地配置文件地址</span></p>\n   <pre><code><pre style=\"border-radius:6px;padding:0px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 0px 2px 8px;margin:24px 0px;overflow:hidden;text-align:left;\"><code style=\"padding:16px 20px;white-space:pre-wrap;display:block;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;SF Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;line-height:1.7;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\"><span leaf=\"\">我的系统中已经安装了Claude Code CLI、Claude Code VS Extension</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">其中Claude Code VS Extension配置文件的地址分别是：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">~/Library/Application Support/Antigravity/User/settings.json</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code的配置文件地址，你自己想办法找，我懒得找了</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">你的任务</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">1. 把Claude Code CLI和Claude Code VS Extension，都改成：使用我们自己的API，而不是通过官方订阅认证。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">2. 默认打开bypassPermissions</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">3. 让我进入的时候，不要弹出提示我登录。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">API是：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"http://localhost:8045/v1/messages\" target=\"_blank\">http://localhost:8045/v1/messages</a></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">curl <a href=\"http://localhost:8045/v1/messages\" target=\"_blank\">http://localhost:8045/v1/messages</a></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">-H \"Content-Type: application/json\"</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">-H \"x-api-key: sk-c103bdb0eae4480aacb2198e69ddfe4a\"</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">-H \"anthropic-version: 2023-06-01\"</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">-d '{</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">\"model\": \"claude-opus-4-5-thinking\",</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">\"max_tokens\": 1024,</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">\"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hello\"}]</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">}'</span></code><br></pre></code><br></pre>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">手动配置：你自己上网搜索吧，既然有了API，就是想办法把API填入到Claude Code的配置文件里就行。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如何找到Claude Code VS Extension的配置文件地址？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如图所示，我是安装到Google Antigravity里了。如果是Cursor和VS Code，原理一样。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8472222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12) 0px 8px 32px;max-height: 600px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016711\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=398bc618&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BFeN9uWkpyaHvDd42pHT4gCpqLFxJv6M8eUTAXewcuGcxdqXoQtYSDXg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">其中，Claude Code VS Extension配置完成后，配置文件大概是长这样的，如下图所示</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6194444444444445\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12) 0px 8px 32px;