<p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5981481481481481\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;border-radius: 4px !important;object-fit: contain !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016715\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=32fcb644&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BFegMg7OVJbhNsOMtYYyrX8pyDG4CFZysgd6J72ARQD3aibnpfAt4N2Mg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5731481481481482\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;border-radius: 4px !important;object-fit: contain !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016714\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a6d48d06&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BFhxibjVRBYeJsicibQiadswZo0cUUXib8bPnar8wrVde9bIkk7S2BSLQHiaicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">注意：可以在Antigravity Tools里查看各个模型的限额，如果购买的是Google AI Ultra套餐，限额比较耐心，5小时刷新一次限额，没有周限额。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5445544554455446\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1010\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12) 0px 8px 32px;max-height: 600px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016712\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6023d473&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BFB10QSicw9YaXCYc16icCPVlrLUnssA7vgE2RQ5qNibZ5FLsjzNfPuWO5A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 36px;font-weight: 600;margin: 56px 0px 28px;letter-spacing: -0.02em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(193, 95, 60) 0%, rgb(157, 200, 141) 100%) text;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">常见问题</span></h2>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;margin: 48px 0px 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: inherit !important;background-color: transparent !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">如何把API共享给团队？</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果团队在内网地址，把API访问地址改成内网地址就行；</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果团队在公网，你可以给API做一个内网穿透，让它拥有公网地址。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么，团队成员所有配置和你相同、不需要下载Google Antigravity和Antigravity Tools，只需要配置的时候把API地址改一下就行。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果团队比较大，可以多买几个Google AI 账号。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: 600;margin: 48px 0px 24px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;line-height: 1.3 !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: inherit !important;background-color: transparent !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">搜索能力怎么办？</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我用的是其他MCP。提供搜索能力的MCP很多，比较好找。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，不配置也没事，因为其实大部分编程过程中也不太需要搜索。请你配置好context7，写代码就足够了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4148148148148148\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12) 0px 8px 32px;max-height: 600px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100016713\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f8aef5d7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlEOKiaDJIeO0hYbdZr60ia2BFicEnDrgL4bGic4pRuIqGicwxptOcs2us53LESlXAQFibJAKtg777TW7xLA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <hr style=\"margin: 64px auto;border: none;height: 2px;background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.3), rgba(157, 200, 141, 0.3), transparent);\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">期待评论区交流！</span></p>\n  </div